I decided to redo my assignment 2, which was a gaming website. I changed the code to only use Bootstrap.

> ⚙️ The entire layout and design rely solely on **Bootstrap utility classes**.

---

### 💻 Technologies Used

- [Bootstrap 5.3](https://getbootstrap.com/)  
- [Font Awesome 6](https://fontawesome.com/) for icons  
- HTML5 (no custom CSS or JS)

---

### ✨ Features

- 📢 **News** — Bootstrap cards with latest headlines  
- 📝 **Reviews** — game analysis cards with background image on hover  
- 📊 **Tables** — console specs comparison, upcoming releases, and rankings  
- 📩 **Contact Form** — clean form with icons and validation  
- 🌙 **Dark theme** with colored highlights (warning/info)

---

### 📱 Responsive Design

The website is fully **mobile-first**, ensuring a great experience on:

- Smartphones  
- Tablets  
- Desktop screens

